drh added on 2019-09-23 11:44:50:
The answer to the query at the end of the following code should be NULL, not 1:
CREATE TABLE t1(x);
INSERT INTO t1(x) VALUES(1);
SELECT (SELECT x FROM t1 LIMIT 0);
The problem was reported on the public mailing list by Justin Ng.  The
problem has been in the code since before version 3.1.0 (2005-01-21).
